      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age. The exterior has some visible scratches and minor dings, and the interior shows signs of regular use with some wear on the upholstery. While the engine and transmission are currently functional, the car will likely need some routine maintenance and minor repairs in the near future to keep it running optimally. It\u2019s a solid choice for someone looking for a budget-friendly option who doesn't mind a bit of character and a few pending projects.",
