    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still looks and feels fantastic on the road? I'm parting with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It runs like a dream and has been really well-cared for, making it perfect for someone who wants a high-quality experience without the brand-new price tag. It's got plenty of life left in it and is ready for its next adventure. Come take it for a spin\u2014I'm sure you'll fall in love with it just like I did!",
