    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2005 BMW M3 (E46) is a meticulously maintained example of high-revving German engineering. It features the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine, equipped with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure VANOS, providing exceptional throttle response up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Mechanical integrity has been prioritized, with documented preventative rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe to address common chassis fatigue. The suspension retains its factory-spec handling characteristics with refreshed bushings and dampers. While the exterior shows minor road patina consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the mechanical components are dialed in for peak performance. An honest, analog machine for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
