    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is the perfect balance of performance and practicality, meticulously maintained to ensure it remains in solid condition for its next owner. The exterior retains its deep luster, with only the minor, expected signs of careful road use. Step inside to find a cabin that has been treated with respect; the upholstery is supple and free of tears, while all electronic features\u2014from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014function exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smooth and quiet, a testament to a life of on-time oil changes and proactive maintenance. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the suspension provides a composed, comfortable ride. Whether you are commuting or heading out on a weekend getaway, this car offers the peace of mind that comes from a vehicle that has been genuinely cared for. It is a turn-key example ready for many more miles of dependable service.",
      "price": 34500.0,
